text:
Or Login / Register With Us Forgot Password? Remember Me ALi gets melancholy in her teaser for collaboration with Super Junior's Yesung By jennywill 10 minutes ago 899 89 2 0 Google+ Yesung and ALi will be having a duet song, and now we have ALi's MV teaser out!
Just like Yesung's teaser from two days ago , ALi is by herself and looks sad in her sun-lit surroundings as she puts an old cassette tape into her player.
